30
00:02:41,330 --> 00:02:43,400
He still looks half-dead.

31
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:46,780
It seems that the marriage did not help. It won't save his life.

32
00:02:46,780 --> 00:02:50,750
But now, the only problem is if Jun Zhenzhen is using the marriage

33
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:53,380
to get pregnant with a male offspring of the Fang family.

34
00:02:53,380 --> 00:02:55,640
What do you mean by that?

35
00:02:59,220 --> 00:03:01,210
If Jun Zhenzhen dies,

36
00:03:01,210 --> 00:03:04,110
where is the Fang family going to find

37
00:03:04,110 --> 00:03:07,310
