No one is going to kill her.

40
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:16,900
It's just that she got unlucky and got into an accident.

41
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:22,620
I'm afraid that this isn't proper.

42
00:03:22,620 --> 00:03:25,600
The Fang family has taken such a fall already.

43
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:28,550
A young girl like Jun Zhenzhen isn't able to stir up any trouble.

44
00:03:28,550 --> 00:03:32,560
Don't you think we should give this matter some more thought?

45
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,590
You're afraid?

46
00:03:35,490 --> 00:03:37,320
We can't turn back now.

47
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:40,920
Even if you're not looking out for yourself, shouldn't you at least be looking out for Jinxiu?

48
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:45,300
Moreover, the success or failure of this plan we've had for over ten years depends on this one action.

49
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:48,850
I know you're sensible.

50
00:03:48,850 --> 00:03:53,120
As long as you do what I say, Jinxiu will be safe and sound.

51
00:03:57,360 --> 00:04:00,940
Madame Su just went out to see someone.

52
00:04:00,940 --> 00:04:05,190
