53
00:04:05,190 --> 00:04:09,330
He made many twists and turns and got rid of the people we sent after him.

54
00:04:09,970 --> 00:04:12,470
I originally thought she had a gentle nature.

55
00:04:12,470 --> 00:04:16,490
Who would've thought that she was a poisonous snake right beside the master's pillow.

56
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:20,280
