130
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:32,880
<i>[Beloved Wife Princess Jiuling from Husband Lu Yunqi]</i>

131
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:37,530
So the only thing I can do now,

132
00:09:38,450 --> 00:09:41,280
