♫ <i>I wouldn’t stop shedding tears like the rain</i> ♫

177
00:16:01,770 --> 00:16:08,280
♫ <i>It’s hard to see you again. I’m wailing in deep sorrow</i> ♫

178
00:16:08,280 --> 00:16:09,680
