245
00:20:27,850 --> 00:20:30,160
Tell us.

246
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:32,000
Can we have the wedding for Chengyu and I,

247
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:35,390
Right after the third day of the third month.

248
00:20:36,850 --> 00:20:39,750
